Muchidzidzo [[fundoyetsimba]], [[mhanda]] (Force) tinoiwona mazuva ose panosundwa kana kuzvuviwa chinhu. Mhanda inokonzera kuchinja kwe[[muchacha]] (speed), kuchinja kwedzivo, kana kuchinja kwemaumbirwo akaita chiumbwa (Shape)zvikuru sei takatarisana nezviumbwa zvisina kusimba. 

Mhanda ine [[tsazaniso]] (equation) inoti F = huremu X [[rufangu]]. 

Mhanda inopimwa nechiyero chinonzi Newton (N).

